<h2>Sore tongue, Swollen tongue, Tenderness to touch and White patches on tongue</h2>
<p>WebMD Symptom Checker helps you find the most common medical conditions indicated by the symptoms sore tongue, swollen tongue, tenderness to touch and white patches on tongue including Hematoma, Giant cell arteritis (temporal arteritis), and Cellulitis.</p>
